collection.description:
Evaverse NFT Collection is a 10,000 1/1 unique ERC-721 set of beautifully animated 3D avatars.  Each avatar is created from up to 19 possible unique traits, creating 430 million total unique variations possible. Certain avatars will possess incredibly rare traits.

Each NFT is a rigged and animated playable game character inside the Evaverse video game.  Evaverse is a multiplayer social game built for the NFT Community.  Evaverse NFT holders will be able to propose and vote on future game updates design mechanics. The game will be launched on Steam following the reveal of the NFTs.

The EVAVERSE video game can be played on [Steam](https://store.steampowered.com/app/1628750/Evaverse). Visit [evaverse.com](https://evaverse.com) for more information
[Evaverse Turtle Troop](https://opensea.io/assets/eva-turtle)

collection.description:
Evaverse NFT Collection is a 10,000 1/1 unique ERC-721 set of beautifully animated 3D avatars.  Each avatar is created from up to 19 possible unique traits, creating 430 million total unique variations possible. Certain avatars will possess incredibly rare traits.

Each NFT is a rigged and animated playable game character inside the Evaverse video game.  Evaverse is a multiplayer social game built for the NFT Community.  Evaverse NFT holders will be able to propose and vote on future game updates design mechanics. The game will be launched on Steam following the reveal of the NFTs.

The EVAVERSE video game can be played on [Steam](https://store.steampowered.com/app/1628750/Evaverse). Visit [evaverse.com](https://evaverse.com) for more information

collection.description: CryptoNewYorkers are a limited release algorithmically generated pixel art collection based on characters from New York City. Available only to IRL visitors of the Bright Moments NY gallery, CryptoNewYorkers grant holders exclusive access to IRL and metaverse experiences. With over 200,000 possible combinations, CryptoNewYorkers represent the diversity of New York City.  Venice and New York are the first of ten CryptoX cities around the world that we will visit in the coming years.  By minting a full 10,000 generative art NFTs IRL, Bright Moments seeks to connect creatively, emotionally and even spiritually, with an international community of artists, collectors and ordinary people who are simply curious about crypto.
